啲啦 我第一次考就係呢條路腳震起唔曬極力子收左皮 小心啲就得 行內街就老虎都讓對面車行先啦 老遠見到佢黎就好停車讓佢 慢慢揸唔洗急 行外圈就無難道基本上無任何犯錯機會"},{"pid":"e3cea5adbb109ded3a159e37a769aa1b09ca1f62","tid":25500,"uid":21273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T15:25:12.000Z","msg":"第一堂學車師傅已經同我講忠義兩難全<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c45066ff2bd70acf98118470fa8f7481ef10c96a","tid":25500,"uid":43231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T15:43:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>分你行迦密村街定兜大圈果條斜路小心啲啦 我第一次考就係呢條路腳震起唔曬極力子收左皮 小心啲就得 行內街就老虎都讓對面車行先啦 老遠見到佢黎就好停車讓佢 慢慢揸唔洗急 行外圈就無難道基本上無任何犯錯機會</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n多謝忠告 會操好d極力子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ed599fda2ee73b7b64ea63da5523ffb63beb1ae","tid":25500,"uid":43231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T15:44:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>第一堂學車師傅已經同我講忠義兩難全<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbc29b3f21960b5eb05646126d94c35b9a74a66c","tid":25500,"uid":14208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T15:46:32.000Z","msg":"忠義唔係最易架咩<br />\n迦密村街過死車處理得好啲就可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一take 忠義街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47aeec7ae1a08df38c4aa771a3700587c1e0360e","tid":25500,"uid":43231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T16:06:43.000Z","msg":"迦密街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個個都提<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 似乎幾惡啃"},{"pid":"fe4a3a17620dfef9a37399b5a2390622f33c80f6","tid":25500,"uid":14208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T16:15:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>迦密街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\